com.facebook.buck.core.graph.transformation

Interface GraphEngineCache<Key extends ComputeKey<Value>,Value extends ComputeResult>

  • Type Parameters:
    Key - Key to the cache
    Value - Value stored by Cache
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    RuleAnalysisCache
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BuildFileManifestCache, DirectoryListCache, FileTreeCache, NoOpGraphEngineCache, RuleAnalysisCacheImpl

    public interface GraphEngineCache<Key extends ComputeKey<Value>,Value extends ComputeResult>
    Interface for a Cache object that GraphTransformationEngine uses to store results that have finished computing so that the results can be reused.

    The cache should be thread safe
